x :str:\n\n  : The prefix path to all routes in the module.\n    Must start, and not end, with `/`.\n\n  module :logiclayer.LogicLayerModule:\n\n  : An instance of a subclass of {class}`logiclayer.LogicLayerModule`.\n\nKeyword arguments:\n\n: {any from {func}`FastAPI.include_router` function}\n"]}, {"name": "logiclayer.logiclayer.LogicLayer.add_redirect", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "url", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Setups a route with the sole purpose of redirecting the user to another location."]}, {"name": "logiclayer.logiclayer.LogicLayer.add_route", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "endpoint", "type": {"name": "CallableMayReturnCoroutine", "xref": {"fqname": "logiclayer.logiclayer.module.CallableMayReturnCoroutine", "project": null}, "params": [{"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Setups a path function to be used directly in the root app.\n\nArguments:\n    path :str:\n        The full path to the route this function will serve.\n    func :Callable[..., Response] | Callable[..., Coroutine[Any, Any, Response]]:\n        The function which will serve the content for the route."]}, {"name": "logiclayer.logiclayer.LogicLayer.add_static", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type"